com.github.mlefeb01.spigotutils.plugin.gui

Class GUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mlefeb01.spigotutils.plugin.gui.GUI

  • public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps a Bukkit inventory and provides additional functionality. The action system is inspired by MassiveCore, it maps menu slots to an action that will be ran when clicked. This allows for easy interactive menu creation without the hassle of identifying different ItemStacks within the menu
